summary: Patch for Falskaar and Qaxe's Questorium. Works with other mods that place a boat near Dawnstar and conflicts with Falskaar, as it only needs Falskaar as a master.
descriptionHtml:
Patch for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37994/]Falskaar[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75451/]Qaxe's Questorium[/url].

The ship is moved to the right.

Works with other mods that place a boat near Dawnstar and conflicts with Falskaar, as it only needs Falskaar as a master.
author: LimitSkies
